                                    the day was Guru Poornima day. They started worshipping Shri Sai Baba as their Guru, and that practice has continued till today not only in Shirdi but all over the world where prayers are offered to Shri Sai.
                                </p>
                                <p class="text-justify"><b>How does one celebrate Guru Poornima? </b></p>
